Let's criticize someone who truly deserves it:<br>
<br>
NO AUTHOR can match PIERS ANTHONY for sheer exploitation of his/her own works.   <br>
<br>
Although I enjoyed the first Xanth novel or two, that entire series was a total waste of paper and my brother's money.  I can't believe that my brother was stupid (I loved and miss my brother.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    ) enough to buy the whole series, much less that I bothered to read every one of the books after he handed them down to me.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
<br>
