<br>
*chuckles*  <br>
<br>
I still think that Piers Anthony shakes his head and clucks his tongue when he thinks about how he suckered so many people into repeatedly paying for the same shit bound in a new cover.  That man is/was pompous.  You just have to read anything non-fiction he wrote in the late 80's to know that he had an ego the size of the moon.  I guarantee he knew exactly what he was doing and enjoyed taking every penny his loyal fans forked over for his self-exploitative drivel.<br>
